[I] A library for reading and writing TIFF files

[T] libtiff is a library for reading and writing data files
[T] encoded with the Tag Image File format, Revision 6.0 (or
[T] revision 5.0 or revision 4.0). This file format is suit-
[T] able for archiving multi-color and monochromatic image
[T] data.

[U] http://www.simplesystems.org/libtiff/

